ated by this last compiler is\nwithin a constant factor of optimal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Dec 2014 02:02:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2015 21:38:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-30"}
