olar twins in our sample, three of which are\npublished here for the first time. Conclusions. Our methods provide an\nindependent means to differentially test the calibration of stellar catalogues\naround the values of a well-known benchmark star, which makes our work\ninteresting for calibration tests of upcoming Galactic surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Dec 2014 14:13:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Feb 2015 14:29:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-11"}
